        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/herohtar/{size}/43780_2.png",
        "created_at": "2021-09-11T21:52:02.477Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The information of who is sending the message and who they are quoting needs to be there.</p>\n<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"jacekk\" data-post=\"4\" data-topic=\"36823\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/jacekk/48/17149_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> jacekk:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This was inspired by FB Messenger, and there it looks like this:</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Note that those messages say ‚ÄúJacek replied to you‚Äù above them ‚Äì it shows who it‚Äôs from and who they are replying to. If they reply to someone else it will say ‚ÄúJacek replied to Herohtar‚Äù, etc.</p>",
